=head1 DESCRIPTION

Inference Recommender provisions SageMaker endpoints with access to VPC
in the inference recommendation job.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> SecurityGroupIds => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The VPC security group IDs. IDs have the form of C<sg-xxxxxxxx>.
Specify the security groups for the VPC that is specified in the
C<Subnets> field.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Subnets => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The ID of the subnets in the VPC to which you want to connect your
model.



